message:
This is about internationalization/localization, probably something that you guys may be interested in as many of you may be required to deliver content in Arabic as well as English

This is a recording from the session "I18n - why, how; and where the name came from" by "Simon Rodwell", recorded live in Sydney JavaScript usergroup gathering June 2013

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xc1dirAxEJg
name: SydJS June 2013 - I18n - why, how; and where the name came from
